":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T15:47:29.000Z","msg":"講得出呢啲說話嘅人係幾咁自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"922d43d6b85d65b4e1dd168196b314c6638a8d93","tid":32812,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T03:42:30.000Z","msg":"老港畜諗嘢真係中國邏輯嚟<br />\n最慘係香港淪陷後果係後生嘅食哂<br />\n唔會報落老港畜度"},{"pid":"42cd3f7f7a087cf8db442598394a472537abcadb","tid":32812,"uid":22544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T03:44:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36a26265a291ad84e1a066fdc9f62f5e1a764ca","tid":32812,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T03:54:29.000Z","msg":"班廢老經歷左港英統治下香港最輝煌既七八十年代<br />\n經濟起飛 成個東南亞都仰望香港<br />\n創業、搞生意易過借火<br />\n班廢心唔知恩圖報不突止<br />\n仲走去奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家香港經濟下滑<br />\n後生仔搵唔到工開<br />\n成班錢已袋就落井下石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n陳雲有句說話真係講得好岩<br />\n如果香港人係一個民族<br />\n佢係人類之恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25a04c1fad8dbce25cb724ae080c5fbc5fa0aca8","tid":32812,"uid":10682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T03:54:36.000Z","msg":"睇到頭幾句已經爆撚哂粗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"284c39fe187cf5651894f47214916da448dffc11","tid":32812,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T03:58:47.000Z","msg":"有咩辦法可以減少廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}